The paper discusses access control mechanisms for web services, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also mentions cloud computing, which is a topic covered in distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper proposes a new policy language, which is a topic covered in software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed language, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
